/** @format */

import React, { Fragment } from "react";
import { Grid, Card, Button, Typography } from "@mui/material";

const MatterCards = () => {
  return (
    <Fragment>
      <Grid container spacing={2} mt={1.5}>
        <Grid item xs={8}>
          <Grid item>
            <Card
              sx={{
                minWidth: 200,
                borderRadius: "1rem",
                backgroundColor: "red",
                color: "white",
              }}
            >
              <Grid container p={3}>
                <Grid item xs={8}>
                  <Typography
                    component="span"
                    sx={{ fontSize: 14 }}
                    gutterBottom
                  >
                    Urgent
                  </Typography>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={4} alignItems="right">
                  <Typography variant="h5" component="h6">
                    0
                  </Typography>
                </Grid>
              </Grid>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item>
            <Card
              sx={{
                minWidth: 200,
                borderRadius: "1rem",
                backgroundColor: "orange",
                color: "white",
              }}
            >
              <Grid container p={3}>
                <Grid item xs={8}>
                  <Typography
                    component="span"
                    sx={{ fontSize: 14 }}
                    gutterBottom
                  >
                    Concern
                  </Typography>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={4} alignItems="right">
                  <Typography variant="h5" component="h6">
                    0
                  </Typography>
                </Grid>
              </Grid>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item>
            <Card
              sx={{
                minWidth: 200,
                borderRadius: "1rem",
                backgroundColor: "green",
                color: "white",
              }}
            >
              <Grid container p={3}>
                <Grid item xs={8}>
                  <Typography
                    component="span"
                    sx={{ fontSize: 14 }}
                    gutterBottom
                  >
                    Start
                  </Typography>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={4} alignItems="right">
                  <Typography variant="h5" component="h6">
                    0
                  </Typography>
                </Grid>
              </Grid>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item>
            <Card
              sx={{
                minWidth: 200,
                borderRadius: "1rem",
                backgroundColor: "white",
                color: "black",
              }}
            >
              <Grid container p={3}>
                <Grid item xs={8}>
                  <Typography
                    component="span"
                    sx={{ fontSize: 14 }}
                    gutterBottom
                  >
                    New
                  </Typography>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={4} alignItems="right">
                  <Typography variant="h5" component="h6">
                    0
                  </Typography>
                </Grid>
              </Grid>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item>
          <Button
            variant="outlined"
            sx={{
              minWidth: 100,
              height: 50,
              borderRadius: "0.5rem",
              backgroundColor: "white",
              color: "black",
            }}
          >
            Import
          </Button>
          <Button
            variant="contained"
            sx={{
              minWidth: 100,
              height: 50,
              borderRadius: "0.5rem",
            }}
          >
            + New
          </Button>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
    </Fragment>
  );
};

export default MatterCards;
